                        </div>
                        <div>
                        <input type="radio" value=60 id="radio_8" name="q3"/>
                        <label for="radio_8" class="radio"><span>Just satisfactorily</span></label>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <input type="radio" value=30 id="radio_9" name="q3"/>
                            <label for="radio_9" class="radio"><span>Very poor communication</span></label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    </div>
                    <br><br>

                    <div class="question">
                    <label>The instructor was well prepared for the class</label>
